msgctxt "56_Officer"
msgid "Oh, Detective Tanimura! Glad you're here."
msgstr "Oh, ¡Detective Tanimura! Me alegro de que esté aquí."

msgctxt "68_Officer"
msgid "It seems the robbery suspects have hidden out in the underground parking lot."
msgstr "Parece que los sospechosos del robo se han escondido en el parking subterráneo."

msgctxt "80_Officer"
msgid "We haven't spotted them yet. They seem really good at staying hidden."
msgstr "No los hemos localizado todavía. Parece que son muy buenos escondiéndose."

msgctxt "92_Officer"
msgid "We could really use your help here."
msgstr "Podríamos usar tu ayuda."

